You can also find a bigger store to stock up on more food like frozen meals and drinks like beer on the way during your daily commute.

When completing the journey to Targoviste, you will be riding your track bike over flat roads getting about an elevation of 3m (10ft) over the 10.11km (6.3 mi) ride. We suggest you turn off your eBike and enjoy the ride as normal, your body weight and speeding legs can help get you over the biking route quite fast. You will be cycling roughly at 47km/h (29 mph), making it easy to cover the 6.3 mile distance in a short time.

From Mala Rumanija, traveling through Muzilov to Lady Mountain, you will see a house made of glass most of the rise. This home can serve as a good reason to stop for soda on the way out. After going back down to the valley floor, you will pass a sign for Caste. The road seems well traveled and may make for some quick biking action.
